*Gray JE (1845). &quot;Catalogue of the Specimens of Lizards in the Collection of the British Museum.&quot; London: Trustees of the British Museum. (Edward Newman, printer). xxviii + 289 pp. (&quot;Anadia&quot;, new genus, p. 58).</text><links>
