<doc id="347893" wikidata="Q642032" url="?curid=347893" title="Leposoma">
<text>Leposoma is a genus of South American lizards in the family Gymnophthalmidae.

==Species==
The following six species are recognized as being valid:
*&quot;Leposoma annectans&quot; 
*&quot;Leposoma baturitensis&quot; 
*&quot;Leposoma nanodactylus&quot; 
*&quot;Leposoma puk&quot; 
*&quot;Leposoma scincoides&quot; - skink tegu
*&quot;Leposoma sinepollex&quot; 

